item.title: Galleria Marchetti Wedding by Jeffrey and Julia Woods
item.description:
Galleria Marchetti Wedding by Jeffrey and Julia Woods

We're totally loving the bits of vintage chic mixed with a dash of whimsy that give this floral filled fete such a unique look. The ladies at Bliss Weddings and Events truly outdid themselves with the design and planning and we can't get enough of the ribbon-tied balloons and pretty mercury glass candlesticks.

item.title: Wedding Style: Classic Tradition, Elegance and Love
item.description:
Wedding Style: Classic Tradition, Elegance and Love

Sometimes, words fail. That is when the memories take over. A classically beautiful wedding from Jeffrey and Julia Woods ... Jeffrey and Julia Woods are to weddings ... what love is to marriage. A team. A fusion of style, emotion and tradition ... with hearts full of passion.
